the player takes on the role of a medjay named bayek and his wife aya  as they work to protect the people of the ptolemaic kingdom during a time of widespread upheaval  the pharaoh  ptolemy xiii  struggles to maintain his rule while harbouring ambitions of expanding his kingdom  his sister  the recently deposed cleopatra  begins marshalling loyalist forces to launch a counter-coup against ptolemy  and frequent incursions into the kingdom by the roman republic under the command of julius caesar lead to fears of an imminent invasion  
bayek's role as a medjay brings him and aya into contact with the secretive forces manipulating these events and into becoming the first assassins 
